## Notes

- Hono has no official docs MCP server; use this project's local MCP or Context7.
- `hono-mcp` and `@hono/mcp` on npm are for building MCP servers with Hono — not for searching Hono docs.
- Hono runs on Cloudflare Workers, Deno, Bun, Node.js, and other runtimes — check `getting-started/` for runtime-specific setup.
